Gigabyte has released its Aorus GTX 1070 Gaming Box, which includes a built-in Nvidia GeForce GTX 1070 card. The device is a plug-and-play external GPU solution and can connect to any compatible device using a Thunderbolt 3 cable. The Gaming Box can also supply a connected device with up to 100W of power and features numerous ports, including HDMI, DisplayPort, DVI, and USB 3.0. Other features include a 450W power supply and dynamic RGB lighting. The Aorus Gaming Box is priced at $599.